                     <interp inst="t17771015-72-off370" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17771015-72-off370" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t17771015-72-person658">
